Setting up Email System:

1)install django-kronos (pip install django-kronos)
2)go to the directery project is located in and migrate the system (python manage.py migrate) 
3)Then install the cron tasks (python manage.py installtasks) 
4)Then you should have a system that every tuesday @10 am send an email of the last week of information
5)Change the my_username, my_password, my_port, my_host in the sendEmail method in cron.py which is located in the app folder to your email credentials(it's at the bottom of the page)
